## 1. Product Overview
Auto-Pick is a simple, comprehensive, easy to use web app with the goal of assisting users in finding their next and/or selling a vehicle. Users make use of the centralized platform to meet their needs. 
Sellers list their vehicles, customers search and save any vehicel they are interested in, until they find the perfect vehicle for them. They can then contact the seller and make a purchase.

